[
  {
    "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
    "speaker_name": "段誉",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "在下单名一誉字，从来没学过什么武艺。我看到别人摔交，不论他真摔还是假摔，忍不住总是要笑的。",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 29,
    "line_end": 29
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
    "speaker_name": "段誉",
    "listener": "char_yue_lao_san",
    "text": "你师父是你的师父，你师父可不是我的师父。你师父差得动你，你师父可差不动我。你师父叫你跟人家比剑，你已经跟人家比过了。你师父叫我跟你比剑，我一来不会，二来怕输，三来怕痛，四来怕死，因此是不比的。我说不比，就是不比。",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 37,
    "line_end": 37
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
    "speaker_name": "段誉",
    "listener": "char_zhong_ling",
    "text": "咱们有福共享，有难同当，瓜子一齐吃，刀剑一块挨。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 185,
    "line_end": 185
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
    "speaker_name": "段誉",
    "listener": "char_zhong_ling",
    "text": "跟你这样美丽的小姑娘一起死了，倒也挺快活。",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 339,
    "line_end": 339
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": "钟灵",
    "listener": "char_duan_yu",
    "text": "你对我倒挺讲义气，赶过来跟我同生共死，你是个好人。",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 339,
    "line_end": 339
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
    "speaker_name": "段誉",
    "listener": "char_mu_wan_qing",
    "text": "婉妹，都是我不好。你别生气，咱们慢慢想法子逃出去。",
    "tone": "恳求",
    "chapter": 7,
    "line_start": 299,
    "line_end": 299
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_jiu_mo_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "鸠摩智",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "小僧当年与慕容先生有约，要借贵门《六脉神剑经》去给他一观。此约未践，一直耿耿于怀。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 11,
    "line_start": 21,
    "line_end": 21
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
    "speaker_name": "段誉",
    "listener": "char_jiu_mo_zhi",
    "text": "你艳羡我段家的六脉神剑剑法，要逼我写出来给你。这件事办不到。",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 11,
    "line_start": 21,
    "line_end": 21
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
    "speaker_name": "段誉",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "你们是我朋友啊！这和尚自恃武功高强，横行霸道的欺侮人。只可惜我不会武功，敌他不过，你们快快走罢。",
    "tone": "焦急",
    "chapter": 11,
    "line_start": 295,
    "line_end": 295
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "乔峰",
    "listener": "char_duan_yu",
    "text": "众位兄弟，我今日好生欢喜，新交了一位好朋友，这位是大理段氏的段誉兄弟，我二人意气相投，已结拜为金兰兄弟。",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 14,
    "line_start": 341,
    "line_end": 341
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "乔峰",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我丐帮开帮数百年，在江湖上受人尊崇，并非恃了人多势众、武功高强，乃是由于行侠仗义、主持公道之故。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 15,
    "line_start": 49,
    "line_end": 49
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "乔峰",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我想慕容复是大英雄、好汉子，不会下手去杀害马二哥。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 15,
    "line_start": 63,
    "line_end": 63
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": "全冠清",
    "listener": "char_xiao_feng",
    "text": "乔峰，你好泰然自若！难道你自己真的不知？",
    "tone": "嘲讽",
    "chapter": 15,
    "line_start": 183,
    "line_end": 183
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "萧峰",
    "listener": "char_a_zhu",
    "text": "从今而后，我是萧峰，不再是乔峰了。",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 21,
    "line_start": 271,
    "line_end": 271
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "萧峰",
    "listener": "char_a_zhu",
    "text": "阿朱，你对我这么好，不以我是契丹贱种而厌弃我么？",
    "tone": "恳求",
    "chapter": 21,
    "line_start": 359,
    "line_end": 359
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_a_zhu",
    "speaker_name": "阿朱",
    "listener": "char_xiao_feng",
    "text": "便跟着你杀人放火，打家劫舍，也永不后悔。跟着你吃尽千般苦楚，万种熬煎，也是欢欢喜喜。",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 21,
    "line_start": 363,
    "line_end": 363
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "萧峰",
    "listener": "char_a_zhu",
    "text": "从今而后，你别再叫我什么大爷、二爷了，你叫我大哥！",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 21,
    "line_start": 367,
    "line_end": 367
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "萧峰",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "阿朱就是阿朱，四海列国，千秋万载，就只一个阿朱。岂是一千个、一万个汉人美女所能代替得了的？",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 49,
    "line_start": 181,
    "line_end": 181
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "萧峰",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "阿朱，阿朱！",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line_start": 163,
    "line_end": 163
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "萧峰",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "不错，是我打死了你姊姊，你该为你姊姊报仇。快，快杀了我罢！",
    "tone": "悲痛",
    "chapter": 23,
    "line_start": 167,
    "line_end": 167
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_a_zi",
    "speaker_name": "阿紫",
    "listener": "char_xiao_feng",
    "text": "姊夫，我不是怕回去受师父责罚，他最多不过杀了我，杀就杀好了。我是舍不得离开你，我要永永远远陪在你身边。",
    "tone": "恳求",
    "chapter": 27,
    "line_start": 179,
    "line_end": 179
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_xu_zhu",
    "speaker_name": "虚竹",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我来解这棋局。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 31,
    "line_start": 199,
    "line_end": 199
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": "苏星河",
    "listener": "char_xu_zhu",
    "text": "胡闹，胡闹，你自填一气，共活变成不活，自己杀死一块白棋，那有这等下棋的？",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 31,
    "line_start": 201,
    "line_end": 201
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_xu_zhu",
    "speaker_name": "虚竹",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "小僧棋艺低劣，胡乱下子，志在救人。这盘棋小僧是不会下的，请老前辈原谅。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 31,
    "line_start": 215,
    "line_end": 215
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_xu_zhu",
    "speaker_name": "虚竹",
    "listener": "char_tian_shan_tong_lao",
    "text": "我以为你是个借尸还魂的老女鬼！",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 35,
    "line_start": 349,
    "line_end": 349
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": "天山童姥",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "你们当我是谁？你姥姥身如女童，难道你们瞎了眼，瞧不出来？",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 35,
    "line_start": 345,
    "line_end": 345
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "萧峰",
    "listener": "char_mu_rong_fu",
    "text": "慕容公子、庄帮主、丁老怪，你们便三位齐上，萧某何惧？",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 41,
    "line_start": 337,
    "line_end": 337
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "萧峰",
    "listener": "char_mu_rong_fu",
    "text": "萧某大好男儿，竟和你这种人齐名！",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 42,
    "line_start": 75,
    "line_end": 75
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
    "speaker_name": "段誉",
    "listener": "char_xiao_feng",
    "text": "大哥，不好了！",
    "tone": "焦急",
    "chapter": 42,
    "line_start": 23,
    "line_end": 23
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "萧峰",
    "listener": "char_duan_yu",
    "text": "三弟，你这六脉神剑尚未纯熟，六门剑法齐使，转换之时中间留有空隙，对方便能乘机趋避。你不妨只使一门剑法试试。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 42,
    "line_start": 15,
    "line_end": 15
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_xuan_ci",
    "speaker_name": "玄慈",
    "listener": "char_xu_zhu",
    "text": "你在寺中二十四年，我竟始终不知你便是我的儿子！",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 42,
    "line_start": 368,
    "line_end": 368
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": "叶二娘",
    "listener": "char_xuan_ci",
    "text": "我不苦！你有苦说不出，那才是真苦。",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 42,
    "line_start": 374,
    "line_end": 374
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_xuan_ci",
    "speaker_name": "玄慈",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "二娘，既已作下了恶业，反悔固然无用，隐瞒也是无用。这些年来，可苦了你啦！",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 42,
    "line_start": 374,
    "line_end": 374
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
    "listener": "char_ye_er_niang",
    "text": "你不肯说，我却知道。只因为这孩儿的父亲，乃是佛门子弟，是一位大大有名的高僧。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 42,
    "line_start": 294,
    "line_end": 294
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_xuan_ci",
    "speaker_name": "玄慈",
    "listener": "char_xu_zhu",
    "text": "虚竹，你自立门户，日后当走侠义正道，约束门人弟子，令他们不致为非作歹，祸害江湖，那便是广积福德资粮，多种善因，在家出家，都是一样。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 42,
    "line_start": 240,
    "line_end": 240
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_mu_rong_bo",
    "speaker_name": "慕容博",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "谋事在人，成事在天！",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 42,
    "line_start": 392,
    "line_end": 392
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
    "speaker_name": "段誉",
    "listener": "char_mu_rong_fu",
    "text": "慕容公子，我善言劝你，荣华富贵，转瞬成空，你就算做成了西夏驸马，再要做大燕皇帝，还不知要杀多少人？",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 45,
    "line_start": 217,
    "line_end": 217
  }
]